PREAMBLE

This license grants broad, perpetual, royalty-free rights for personal,
family, educational, and self-study use while strictly protecting the
Work from unauthorized commercial exploitation. Any unlicensed
commercial use triggers automatic, non-negotiable penalties that follow
the product in perpetuity.


DEFINITIONS

"Personal Use" means use by any individual or their immediate family
for non-commercial purposes (including private study, hobby projects,
or home use).

"Educational Use" means use by schools, universities, teachers,
students, or self-learners for teaching, learning, research, or
self-study. Free when no financial gain is derived from the Work itself.

"Commercial Use" means any use that generates revenue, profit, or
commercial advantage, including cloud services, SaaS, hosted platforms,
secondary redistribution for fee, consulting services, product
development, training courses sold for money, or any derivative work
sold or licensed for profit.

"Financial Gain" means any direct or indirect monetary benefit (tuition
fees, subscriptions, consulting revenue, product sales, advertising,
etc.) arising from the use or derivative of the Work.

"Unlicensed Use" means any Commercial Use without a prior written
commercial license from the Licensor.


GRANT OF RIGHTS (FREE USES)

Subject to the conditions below, the Licensor grants you a perpetual,
worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free license to:

  - Use, study, modify, and run the Work for Personal Use and
    Educational Use.

  - Create and distribute derivative works for Personal Use and
    Educational Use (including in classrooms, open-source educational
    repositories, or personal portfolios), provided the original
