Individual and family use is always free. Schools and educational
institutions may use the Work freely as a teaching or research tool.
Self-study is always free. These rights are granted IN PERPETUITY and
cannot be revoked.


COMMERCIAL, CLOUD, AND SECONDARY USE

Any Commercial Use, cloud deployment, SaaS offering, secondary
redistribution, or any use that produces Financial Gain is EXPRESSLY
PROHIBITED without a separate commercial license obtained in advance
from the Licensor.

To obtain a commercial license, contact the Licensor via
https://github.com/tensorrent.

Commercial licenses will include:

  - Negotiated terms specific to the intended use.

  - A royalty share of [X%] (default 5%) of gross revenue derived from
    the Work or any derivative, payable in perpetuity to the Licensor
    and their legal successors or heirs.

  - The royalty obligation survives any transfer of rights and binds
    all future owners or licensees.

Schools or educational entities that derive Financial Gain from the
Work (e.g., selling paid courses, certification programs, or consulting
services based on SIP) must obtain a commercial license and pay the
royalty on those gains.


AUTOMATIC PENALTIES FOR UNLICENSED USE

If the Work or any derivative is used commercially without a prior
license (Unlicensed Use), the following automatic, non-negotiable
penalties apply immediately and in perpetuity:

  - An automatic 4.2% OF GROSS REVENUE from the product or service is
    payable to the Licensor as a distrust fee. This fee is
    non-negotiable and cannot be waived, reduced, or renegotiated.

  - An additional 4.2% OF GROSS REVENUE is payable directly to public
    infrastructure projects designated by the Licensor (or their
    successors) as reparation to the public good.

  - These combined 8.4% obligations attach to the product itself and
    follow it in perpetuity. They survive bankruptcy, sale, transfer of
    ownership, dissolution of the company, or any other attempt to
    evade the obligation unless explicitly released in writing by the
    Licensor or their legal successors.

  - The obligation binds all downstream users, licensees, and owners of
    any product or service that incorporates the Work or a derivative.


OTHER USES

Any use not explicitly granted above (government, military, non-profit
monetized activities, etc.) requires prior written review and licensing
