SUCCESSION

All royalty rights, distrust-fee obligations, and reparation obligations
are perpetual and shall automatically pass to the Licensor's legal
successors or designated heirs. No sale, bankruptcy, or corporate
restructuring can extinguish them unless the Licensor's successors
explicitly agree in writing.


TERMINATION

Any violation of the commercial-use, royalty, or penalty provisions
